data.description: Home Sweet Home!! You must see this spacious 5-bedroom, 3 and half bathrooms home sitting on a picture-perfect yard! Split bedroom plan with huge master bedroom suite located on main floor alongside 2 large secondary bedrooms - two additional bedrooms with a full bathroom upstairs.  Previous home of Builder, this home is loaded with spacious rooms and bells and whistles: dual heating and air units; multiple square columns; arched doorways; vaulted ceilings; catwalk over hardwood two-story foyer; wide hallways; bay windows; thick crown molding and judges panel in formal dining room; ironing board wall cabinet; and side entry garage are just some of this home's bells and whistles! This huge beauty sits on approximately a one-acre corner lot with an immaculate, well-manicured and landscaped lawn enclosed by an upgraded white privacy fence! Located in the sought-after Ola school district! Hurry this property and it's yard/lawn is a must see!!
